{"tid":1983503,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"耿爽: 美方停止向世衛捐助資金是典型威脅訛詐","createTime":"2020-04-22T01:08:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-22T11:24:39.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":67,"uniUserReply":60,"replies":[{"pid":"2b61f120fbab4123d41b44edbbe67261364a6537","tid":1983503,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T01:08:28.000Z","msg":"在北京，外交部發言人耿爽表示，美方近期攻擊指責世衛的言行，中方已經表明立場，指美國自恃世衛最大出資國，認為世衛應該聽其指揮，是典型的霸權心態。世衛堅持客觀公正，對美方不予迎合，美方就停止捐助資金，是典型的威脅訛詐，美方對世衛的攻擊抹黑，沒有事實依據，施壓脅迫更是不得人心。<br />\n<br />\n耿爽又說，世衛在上周末發起網上慈善音樂會，為醫護工作人員募捐，獲得極大關注，反映國際社會的主流民意，中方希望美方一些人，能夠觀看這場音樂會的片段，感受各方支持世衛、呼籲團結協作的普遍願望，不要站在國際社會的對立面。<br />\n<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1521895_1_20200421185000.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1521895_1_20200421185000.jpg&h=40eeef80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1521895-20200421.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1521895-20200421.htm&d=ltyh5TmdzGcNJFTF%2BAmR8mWYsxP5Z0Wle18NOkmjjC4%3D&h=c2a076c1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1521895-20200421.htm&h=73d5fd0c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1521895-20200421.htm</a>"},{"pid":"ce75f985235231d5a662c395f9edc6b279602148","tid":1983503,"uid":261849,"like":32,"dislike":1,"score":31,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T01:11:51.000Z","msg":"點解支那人都識講主流民意依個字.....<br />\n佢有冇了解香港人嘅主流民意呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76d8e0034dd7d6c90be1fe6e7f8f454e88e540cc","tid":1983503,"uid":190005,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T01:16:45.000Z","msg":"人地唔捐錢係人地既內政, 關你撚事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54d1451771f4d5